          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜维上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一颗明珠土内藏，几载未曾放毫光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，姓姜名维字伯约。正在后帐观看兵书，忽听都督免战高悬，不知为了何事？\n不免进帐问个明白。\n报——姜维告进。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜维挖入。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督在上，末将参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马遵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马遵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军无令，进帐何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "末将正在后帐观看兵书，忽听都督免战高悬，不知为了何事？\n马遵 （白 适才探马报道，今有赵云，刀劈韩德父子五人落马，故而免战高悬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督赐某一支将令，生擒赵云入帐！\n马遵 （白 将军有此胆量？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有此胆量！\n马遵 （白 姜维听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马遵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领本部人马，大战赵云，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马遵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令出山摇动，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言发鬼神惊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马遵、四龙套同下。四下手自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立两厢，听某令下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姜伯约在教场忙传令号，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声众三军细听根苗：\n全凭着五虎将立下功劳。\n他三弟张翼德喝断了当阳桥。\n还有个老黄忠会使大刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这一概五虎将俱已丧了，\n只剩下赵子龙老迈年高。\n有关兴与张苞哪放心梢？\n杀子龙擒孔明就在今朝！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜维、四下手同下。）"
        }
      ],
